---
// StorySection.astro — V3 "Paper & Grain"
// Wide typographic spread, no image, pullquote centred, 2-column body
// Section 01 — Our Story
---

<section id="story" class="v3-section v3-story" aria-labelledby="story-heading">

  <!-- Top rule -->
  <hr class="v3-rule" aria-hidden="true" />

  <!-- Section number decorative -->
  <div class="v3-story__number-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="v3-section-number">—01—</span>
  </div>

  <!-- Pullquote — centred, large italic -->
  <blockquote class="v3-story__pullquote v3-reveal">
    <p>
      «&thinsp;The most profound hospitality is not about service.<br />
      It is about place.&thinsp;»
    </p>
  </blockquote>

  <hr class="v3-rule v3-story__mid-rule" aria-hidden="true" />

  <!-- Section heading (visually hidden — pullquote carries the heading) -->
  <h2 id="story-heading" class="v3-story__heading v3-reveal">
    Our Story
  </h2>

  <!-- Two-column body text -->
  <div class="v3-story__body v3-reveal">
    <p>
      Green Horizon began with a walk. An unplanned detour off the main road south of Balchik,
      through a belt of old oak and hornbeam, that ended abruptly at a cliff edge.
      Below: the Black Sea. Above: open sky. Between: nothing but wind and a long way down.
    </p>

    <p>
      The family that owns this land has farmed it, planted it, and argued over it for four generations.
      The decision to build a hotel here was not taken lightly. It took eighteen months of family
      meetings, three architects, and one very stubborn structural engineer who kept insisting
      the cliff was not going anywhere.
    </p>

    <p>
      He was right. The cliff has been here since the Eocene epoch. It will outlast all of us.
      The hotel we are building acknowledges that. It does not compete with the landscape —
      it observes it. Every room faces the sea. Every terrace is positioned for the morning light.
    </p>

    <p>
      We are not in the hospitality industry. We are a family who found a place so improbable,
      so far from what the travel brochures call the Bulgarian coast, that we felt obliged
      to share it — carefully, and only with people who will understand what it is.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="v3-story__cta v3-reveal">
    <a href="#build" class="v3-text-link" aria-label="Follow the progress of the build">
      Follow the build →
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Bottom rule -->
  <hr class="v3-rule v3-story__bottom-rule" aria-hidden="true" />

</section>

<style>
  .v3-story {
    background-color: var(--v3-bg);
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  /* Section number — flush right, huge, muted */
  .v3-story__number-wrap {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 2.5rem 0 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Pullquote — centred, very large */
  .v3-story__pullquote {
    margin: 3.5rem auto 3rem;
    max-width: 860px;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .v3-story__pullquote p {
    font-family: var(--font-v3-primary);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--v3-ink);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .v3-story__mid-rule {
    margin: 0 0 3rem;
  }

  /* Section heading — large but below the pullquote, feels like a kicker */
  .v3-story__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-v3-primary);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--v3-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  /* Two-column body text */
  .v3-story__body {
    column-count: 2;
    column-gap: 4rem;
    column-rule: 1px solid var(--v3-rule);
    max-width: 1040px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .v3-story__body p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 1.4em;
    break-inside: avoid;
  }

  .v3-story__body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .v3-story__cta {
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .v3-story__bottom-rule {
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Mobile ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .v3-story__body {
      column-count: 1;
    }

    .v3-story__pullquote {
      margin: 2.5rem auto 2rem;
    }

    .v3-story__cta {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
